      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC BOCCA (2) clocked a useful 25.41 when placed over 450m at Warrnambool last start in a R/A FIN. Expected to push the clock again here. ENGELKE ROAD (6) has been in super consistent form recently with three minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (42.36) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Cannot be taken lightly. TORNADO TESSA (3) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only one length from Mr. Mocha in second (29.85) at this track. Leading chance. UNLEASH THE LION (1) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
